### =============================================================================
### Data API Builder — REST API Examples
### CSA-in-a-Box | Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### =============================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### ─── GET: All Data Products ────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── GET: Products filtered by domain ──────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?$filter=domain eq 'finance'
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── GET: Products sorted by quality (descending) ──────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?$orderby=quality_score desc
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── GET: Combined filter + sort + pagination ──────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?$filter=status eq 'active'&$orderby=quality_score desc&$first=10
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── GET: Search by name (contains) ────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?$filter=contains(name, 'Revenue')
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── GET: Single product by ID ─────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/id/1
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── POST: Create a new data product ───────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-MS-API-ROLE: authenticated

{
  "name": "Customer Segments",
  "description": "Customer segmentation based on purchase behavior and demographics",
  "domain": "marketing",
  "owner_name": "Dan Wilson",
  "owner_email": "dan@contoso.com",
  "owner_team": "Marketing Insights",
  "classification": "internal",
  "quality_score": 82.5,
  "freshness_hours": 24,
  "completeness": 90.0,
  "status": "draft",
  "version": 1
}

### ─── PUT: Update an existing product ───────────────────────────────────────
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/id/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-MS-API-ROLE: authenticated

{
  "quality_score": 93.0,
  "freshness_hours": 12,
  "version": 3
}

### ─── DELETE: Remove a product ──────────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/id/99
Content-Type: application/json
X-MS-API-ROLE: admin

### ─── GET: All domains ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/domains
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── GET: Quality metrics for product 1 ────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/quality-metrics?$filter=product_id eq 1&$orderby=date desc
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── GET: Access grants (authenticated — sees own) ─────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/access-grants
Content-Type: application/json
X-MS-API-ROLE: authenticated

### ─── GET: Domain stats (stored procedure) ──────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/domain-stats
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── GET: Quality trend (stored procedure) ─────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/quality-trend?product_id=1&days=30
Content-Type: application/json

### ─── GET: Data lineage ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/lineage
Content-Type: application/json
X-MS-API-ROLE: authenticated
